Popular British model and actress, Naomi Elaine Campbell has welcomed her first child at 50. The actress took to her Instagram account on Tuesday to share the good news with her fans and well-wishers. “A beautiful little blessing has chosen me to be her mother and I am so honoured to have this gentle soul in my life. “There are no words to describe the lifelong bond that I bow share with you, my angel. There is no greater love,” she wrote. Meanwhile, celebrities and fans have taken to the comment section of her post to send congratulatory messages to the new mother. 